    <item>
      <title>据称日本将考虑发行期限较短的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/japan-is-said-to-consider-issuing-bonds-with-shorter-maturities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份提案草案显示，日本财务省正在考虑将更多债券发行转向期限较短的债券，这是日本央行削减政府债券购买规模的重大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/japan-is-said-to-consider-issuing-bonds-with-shorter-maturities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英力士创始人亿万富翁拉特克利夫抨击欧洲化学工业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/billionaire-ratcliffe-slams-europe-s-chemical-industry-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业巨头英力士集团 (Ineos Group) 的创始人兼首席执行官、亿万富翁吉姆·拉特克利夫 (Jim Ratcliffe) 表示，高昂的能源和碳成本让欧洲石化行业难以与世界其他地区竞争。拉特克利夫在接受彭博社记者弗朗辛·拉夸 (Francine Lacqua) 采访时表示：“每个人都在离开欧洲的石化行业，这是我工作生涯中从未见过的。”(来源：彭博社)]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/billionaire-ratcliffe-slams-europe-s-chemical-industry-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将抨击法国预算赤字，加剧政治困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/eu-to-slam-france-over-budget-deficit-adding-to-political-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在立法选举开始前不到两周，欧盟将对法国违反欧盟赤字和债务规则进行谴责，此举可能导致高额罚款，并使竞选重点复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/eu-to-slam-france-over-budget-deficit-adding-to-political-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
