    <item>
      <title>中国研究实施央行债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/china-studying-implementation-of-pboc-bond-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行行长潘功胜表示，央行正在与财政部研究如何实施国债交易。但他否认这种做法等同于量化宽松。彭博电视台记者刘敏敏报道。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/china-studying-implementation-of-pboc-bond-trading</guid>
